        "created_at": "2026-02-28T17:04:49.495Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I asked Mary Margaret - 0.24 hectare is the total area purchased, but that includes service paths. Planted vine area is roughly 0.17 hectare - which is where her number comes from for the announcement email from Karolus. She also confirmed it is the plot in Batard Montrachet just below Lafon and DRC\u2019S Montrachet.</p>",
